IMO we should move away from these dynamic connections. My suggestion is to move to the constructor:
```cpp
connect(ui->prune, &QCheckBox::stateChanged, [this](int state) {
    setSizeWarningLabel(/* isPruning = */ state == 2, m_blockchain_size, m_chain_state_size);
});
```

